  <p>more topics: univeral sets of connectives

    facts: every logical connective has a Boolean function

    every Boolean function <m>f\colon \B^n \to \B</m>
    in n variables is expressible as a polynomial
       <m>\sum_I c_I x_1^{i_1}x_2^{i_2}\cdots x_n^{i_n}</m> where
     <m>I=i_1,i_2,\ldots,i_n</m> is a bit string
  </p>
  
<p>Exercises.</p>


</section>
